This template stores an income record in the <code>Income</code> [[Special:CargoTables/Income|Cargo table]]. Pages are normally created and edited via [[Form:Income]] rather than by hand. See [[Help:Receipts]].

Each income entry has 0 or 1 <code>file</code> (the receipt the parser extracted these fields from — typically an invoice or payment confirmation) and 0+ <code>supplemental_files</code> (unparsed supporting documents). A blank <code>file</code> means a manual entry.

The <code>income_category</code> parameter (stored in the <code>category</code> Cargo column) holds a full hierarchical path (e.g. <code>Sales/Products</code>); the vocabulary lives at [[Project:Income categories]]. <code>assignee</code> blank means company-wide.
[[Category:Receipt templates]]
